Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: energetic ray global observatory daemon
 This program interfaces your computer with a compatible ergo unit via serial port. It then uses the board to collect cosmic ray data log it to /etc/ERGO_DATA.csv and send the events to the server For more information join #ERGO-telescope on freenode or go to www.ergotelescope.org
